  • Enclosing class:
    PopulateChunkEvent

    public static class PopulateChunkEvent.Pre
extends PopulateChunkEvent
    PopulateChunkEvent.Pre is fired just before a chunk is populated a terrain feature.
    This event is fired just before terrain feature generation in ChunkProviderEnd#populate(int, int), ChunkProviderOverworld#populate(int, int), and ChunkProviderHell#populate(int, int).

    This event is not Cancelable.

    This event does not have a result. HasResult

    This event is fired on the MinecraftForge.EVENT_BUS.
